{{電遊歷史}}
在电子游戏历史上，'''第七世代'''是指2005年后任天堂、微软和索尼的各自推出的三款家用游戏机。即索尼[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、任天堂[[Wii|Wii]]和微软[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]。

每一款游戏平台都带来突破性的技术。<ref>{{cite web|last=Wisniowski|first=Howard|url=http://www.analog.com/en/press-release/May_09_2006_ADI_Nintendo_Collaboration/press.html|title=Analog Devices And Nintendo Collaboration Drives Video Game Innovation With iMEMS Motion Signal Processing Technology|publisher=Analog Devices, Inc.|date=9 May 2006|accessdate=2006-05-10|archive-date=2015-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107180246/http://www.analog.com/en/press-release/May_09_2006_ADI_Nintendo_Collaboration/press.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==家用机==
=== Wii ===
任天堂以Wii的新方式进入了这一世代。公司计划通过新的游戏体验和游戏互动方式，来吸引目前的核心和休闲玩家<ref>{{cite news|last=Morris |first=Chris |title=Nintendo continues to play coy |publisher=CNN |date=May 9, 2006 |url=http://money.cnn.com/2006/05/09/technology/e3_nintendo/index.htm |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fV21iwH5?url=http://money.cnn.com/2006/05/09/technology/e3_nintendo/index.htm |archivedate=March 23, 2009 |accessdate=December 12, 2007 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、非玩家<ref>{{cite news | last =Hermida | first =Alfred | title =Nintendo shows new games console | publisher =BBC News | date =May 10, 2006 | url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/4756625.stm | accessdate =December 12, 2007 | archive-date =2017-08-10 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170810133427/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/4756625.stm | dead-url =no }}</ref>和曾经的游戏玩家，而不是尖端的图形和昂贵的技术。<ref name="autogenerated2">{{cite news | last =Hartley | first =Matt | title =Reginald Fils-Aime: Nintendo goes for wild ride | publisher =[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]] | date =December 10, 2007 | url =https://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20071210.wdecisionPOINT1208/BNStory/Technology/home | accessdate =December 12, 2007 | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20071215233822/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20071210.wdecisionPOINT1208/BNStory/Technology/home | archivedate =2007年12月15日 }}</ref> 

